First Department,

March, 1959

(March 3, 1959) In the Matter of the Accounting of Chemical Corn Exchange Bank et al., as Trustees under the Will of William C. Herrick, Deceased. Elizabeth K. Abbott et al., Appellants; John J. Fields, 3rd, as Cotrustee, Respondent.

Order of June 30, 1958 unanimously affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements of this appeal to the respondent. No opinion. Order of January 7, 1959 unanimously affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements of this appeal to the respondent. No opinion. Concur — Botein, P. J., M. M. Frank, McNally and Stevens, JJ.
